# Login Bug Reports

---

## BUG-01: User is logged in with invalid password

Title: User is logged in with invalid password

Preconditions:
- Login page is open
- User is registered in the system

Steps to reproduce:
1. Enter valid username
2. Enter invalid password
3. Click "Login"

Expected result:
- Error message "Invalid password" is displayed
- User is not logged in

Actual result:
- User is logged in successfully
- User is redirected to the home page

Severity: High  
Priority: High

---

## BUG-02: No error message for empty fields

Title: No validation message when fields are empty

Preconditions:
- Login page is open

Steps to reproduce:
1. Leave username empty
2. Leave password empty
3. Click "Login"

Expected result:
- Validation messages are shown for required fields

Actual result:
- No error message is displayed
- Nothing happens after clicking Login

Severity: Medium  
Priority: Medium

---

## BUG-03: Login works with spaces in username

Title: Login succeeds with username containing leading/trailing spaces

Preconditions:
- User is registered
- Login page is open

Steps to reproduce:
1. Enter username with spaces (e.g. " user ")
2. Enter valid password
3. Click "Login"

Expected result:
- System trims spaces OR rejects invalid format

Actual result:
- User is logged in successfully without trimming input

Severity: Low  
Priority: Low
